{
  "texts": [
    "New publications are built upon algorithms and tools not only from within the materials science community but also from the computer science community.",
    "This has led to rapid advancements in performance on benchmark tasks such as those in the matbench protocol.",
    "Despite the challenges, outstanding challenges and questions still remain.",
    "In an age where model size and data set size translates directly to performance, what will be the role of individual research labs?",
    "The situation today is that few academic groups have the resources to reproduce state-of-the-art results from industry in many areas of machine learning, making the issue of access and reproducibility particularly concerning at the current moment."
  ]
}